These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, quad-bike, ship
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero, comedy, satire
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine, amber, white
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, chinchilla, shipcher
House: modern, wooden, cape-cod, art-deco
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, azalea, zinnia
 1. the owner of the shipcher is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is the modern house##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person driving the ship is the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who growsmarigold and the art-deco house##2
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person watching satire movies##2
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
12. the owner of the shipcher is the person who likes white##1
13. the cape-cod house is between the wooden house and the person who likes amber##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Transport      | ship        | bike       | quad-bike  | roller |
| Movie-Genre          | satire     | comedy         | superhero     | mystery    |
| Color         | aquamarine  | green      | amber   | white     |
| Pet           | mouse | rabbit | chinchilla   | shipcher     |
| House   | wooden    | cape-cod         | modern | art-deco         |
| Flower         | zinnia     | marigold     | tulip  | azalea       |

