House: colonial, cottage, art-deco, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, cricket, sailing
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, pony, fish
 1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the rat##2
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person eating papaya and the owner of the pony##2
 5. the colonial house is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the owner of the pony is between the person who likes purple and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 9. the person who likes grey is the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
11. the colonial house is the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the person eating apple is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
13. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
14. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
